</div>


    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">
        <strong>07 July 1942</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">Volume 381</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="debateContent">
                <div class="highlightedSearchTerms"></div>
                <div class="content-container">


<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9 hs_ColumnNumber content-container " >
                <span data-toggle="tooltip" data-hop-debug-tooltip class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign hidden hidden-xs" data-placement="bottom" title=" hs_ColumnNumber "></span>

<p class="hs_ColumnNumber"><span id="636" class="column-number column-only" data-column-number="636"></span></p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div>

<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-80ea7691-2dc5-4af9-9397-67c27601a2af'>
            
<p class="">45.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-9aea7af8-8755-4e08-ae11-8a61f601af32">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-9aea7af8-8755-4e08-ae11-8a61f601af32">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-9aea7af8-8755-4e08-ae11-8a61f601af32">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-9aea7af8-8755-4e08-ae11-8a61f601af32">
                Major C. S. Taylor
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9aea7af8-8755-4e08-ae11-8a61f601af32" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-07-07/debates/1bd1b63f-98ee-473b-9bc7-ca0d60204715/ArmyAndAirForce(Co-Operation)#contribution-9aea7af8-8755-4e08-ae11-8a61f601af32">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister whether the aircraft allocated to General Auchinleck for the campaign now being fought in the Middle East are under his direct command for operations?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-9aea7af8-8755-4e08-ae11-8a61f601af32" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-07-07/debates/1bd1b63f-98ee-473b-9bc7-ca0d60204715/ArmyAndAirForce(Co-Operation)#contribution-9aea7af8-8755-4e08-ae11-8a61f601af32">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-920c6d8a-8d16-4b2c-b919-f50dc2de75e8">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-920c6d8a-8d16-4b2c-b919-f50dc2de75e8">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-920c6d8a-8d16-4b2c-b919-f50dc2de75e8">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-920c6d8a-8d16-4b2c-b919-f50dc2de75e8">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-920c6d8a-8d16-4b2c-b919-f50dc2de75e8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-07-07/debates/1bd1b63f-98ee-473b-9bc7-ca0d60204715/ArmyAndAirForce(Co-Operation)#contribution-920c6d8a-8d16-4b2c-b919-f50dc2de75e8">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">On 7th October, 1941, before the winter battle in Libya, I gave a ruling on this subject as follows:—<p></p> "Upon the Military Commander-in-Chief in the Middle East announcing that a battle is in prospect, the Air Officer Commanding-in-Chief will give him all possible aid irrespective of other targets, however attractive. The Army Commander-in-Chief will specify to the Air Officer Commanding-in-Chief the targets and tasks which he requires to be performed, both in the preparatory attack on the rearward installations of the enemy and for air action during the progress of the battle. It will be for the Air Officer Commanding-in-Chief to use his maximum force for these objects in the manner most effective. This applies not only to any squadrons assigned to army co-operation permanently, but also to the whole air force available in the theatre."<p></p> This direction is agreeable to both Services and has been in force ever since.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-920c6d8a-8d16-4b2c-b919-f50dc2de75e8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-07-07/debates/1bd1b63f-98ee-473b-9bc7-ca0d60204715/ArmyAndAirForce(Co-Operation)#contribution-920c6d8a-8d16-4b2c-b919-f50dc2de75e8">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-aa5d1018-6a03-4e11-807d-6be1abe79311">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-aa5d1018-6a03-4e11-807d-6be1abe79311">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-aa5d1018-6a03-4e11-807d-6be1abe79311">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-aa5d1018-6a03-4e11-807d-6be1abe79311">
                Mr. Bellenger
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-aa5d1018-6a03-4e11-807d-6be1abe79311" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-07-07/debates/1bd1b63f-98ee-473b-9bc7-ca0d60204715/ArmyAndAirForce(Co-Operation)#contribution-aa5d1018-6a03-4e11-807d-6be1abe79311">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Will my right hon. Friend consider the desirability of something stronger and more effective than even a direction from him? Would it not be desirable for these two Services even before battle is joined to act in closer co-operation in training than they are doing at the present time?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-aa5d1018-6a03-4e11-807d-6be1abe79311" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-07-07/debates/1bd1b63f-98ee-473b-9bc7-ca0d60204715/ArmyAndAirForce(Co-Operation)#contribution-aa5d1018-6a03-4e11-807d-6be1abe79311">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-770d0441-b372-4c1e-9c1e-47b6b65a8c58">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-770d0441-b372-4c1e-9c1e-47b6b65a8c58">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-770d0441-b372-4c1e-9c1e-47b6b65a8c58">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-770d0441-b372-4c1e-9c1e-47b6b65a8c58">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-770d0441-b372-4c1e-9c1e-47b6b65a8c58" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-07-07/debates/1bd1b63f-98ee-473b-9bc7-ca0d60204715/ArmyAndAirForce(Co-Operation)#contribution-770d0441-b372-4c1e-9c1e-47b6b65a8c58">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I have carefully considered this matter and taken a great deal of different opinions on the subject, and the result, as I believe, has been satisfactory.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-770d0441-b372-4c1e-9c1e-47b6b65a8c58" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
