        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-8f3aeecb-e6dd-44dc-9c1f-e857c5a93273">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8f3aeecb-e6dd-44dc-9c1f-e857c5a93273" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-07-07/debates/1bd1b63f-98ee-473b-9bc7-ca0d60204715/ArmyAndAirForce(Co-Operation)#contribution-8f3aeecb-e6dd-44dc-9c1f-e857c5a93273">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">If my hon. Friend read my statement at leisure, he will see that I go further than that. The entire <span id="638" class="column-number" data-column-number="638"></span> Air Force is subordinated to the purposes of the military commander; he says what he wants them to do, but naturally you must not interfere with the characteristics of a particular arm. How the purposes are carried out is a matter for the Air Officer Commanding.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-8f3aeecb-e6dd-44dc-9c1f-e857c5a93273" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-07-07/debates/1bd1b63f-98ee-473b-9bc7-ca0d60204715/ArmyAndAirForce(Co-Operation)#contribution-8f3aeecb-e6dd-44dc-9c1f-e857c5a93273">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





